Thanks , Kerry . That's what I thought . Michelle Ben: As we discussed , the regulations from the department of labor specifically allow the employment of 14 to 16 year olds in non-hazardous employment . The regulations , however , restrict employment to 40 hours in a week , 8 hours in a day , and between the hours of 7:00 am to 9:00 pm . 29 C.F.R . 570.35 . Thus , don't take the interns to a power plant and don't work them past 9:00 or the hours indicated and you should be ok . Let me know if you have any follow up questions . Littler Mendelson , PC 1900 Chevron Tower 1301 McKinney Street Houston , Texas 77010 713.951.9212 ( fax ) This email may contain confidential and privileged material for the sole use of the intended recipient(s) . Any review , use , distribution or disclosure by others is strictly prohibited . If you are not the intended recipient ( or authorized to receive for the recipient) , please contact the sender by reply email and delete all copies of this message . To reply to our email administrator directly , send an email to
